{"tid":1592300,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國工程院士：推算國內非洲豬瘟的直接損失一萬億人仔","createTime":"2019-09-24T14:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:26:15.000Z","uid":48083,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"808f9cdd705950055209975b1b8b1d9153fc1b64","tid":1592300,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"【財新網】（記者 孫良滋）「據推算國內非洲豬瘟的直接損失有一萬億」，9月24日，中國工程院院士李德發在一個豬業論壇上表示，「這還不算產業鏈的上游和下游」。<br />\n<br />\n　　李德發介紹，進入2010年以來，我國豬肉產量進入5000萬噸的量級，2017年產量是5451萬噸，當年豬肉進口的數量僅為121萬噸、出口量5.13萬噸 ，即基本靠國內的產量滿足國內需求，「全世界的豬一半是由中國產的，非洲豬瘟給畜牧業上了一課，搞不好防疫防病是不行的，這堂課的代價太大」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.companies.caixin.com/m/2019-09-24/101465678.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.companies.caixin.com%2Fm%2F2019-09-24%2F101465678.html&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=4e88037b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.companies.caixin.com/m/2019-09-24/101465678.html</a>"},{"pid":"26ec056301af18df2b28e39aee0973ccd1636ac7","tid":1592300,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"58716ae9a5e61bd8d9d1f57d10d35d4a5b325329","tid":1592300,"uid":70973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[突發]930三罷 文宣工作立即開始!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592295</a>"},{"pid":"69bda5af780639a4c3e504faf96d4b200765c5f1","tid":1592300,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:14:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-larg